Adverse reactions are further classified within body system categories and enumerated in order of decreasing frequency using the following definitions:

  frequentadverse reactions are defined as those occurring in at least 1/100 patients;

  infrequentadverse reactions are those occurring in 1/100 to 1/1,000 patients;

  rareadverse reactions are those occurring in fewer than 1/1,000 patients.
